  Class using parent state:

  ```jome
  // A question mark when dependent on a state or an exclamation mark (silent vs throw exception?)
  class ColoredText |@text, %theme?| {
    print: () => {
      return `<p style="color: {%theme.textColor}">{%theme}</p>`
    }
  }
  ```

  Class having state:

  ```jome
